# Local-only internal monitoring dashboard. NEVER commit any of it: it is a
# local tool that reads production data, and dashboard/server/lexicon.cjs holds
# a moderation slur list that must not enter the repo. Excluding the whole dir
# also keeps it out of EAS uploads (EAS respects .gitignore when no .easignore
# is present). It is additionally blocked from Metro bundling in metro.config.js.
dashboard/
